<template>
  <a-form :form="productAttrForm" layout="horizontal" hideRequiredMark>
    <a-row>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="公差等级"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-select
            v-if="disabled"
            allowClear
            placeholder="请输入公差等级"
            v-decorator="['productAttrlevel']"
          >
            <a-select-option key="0">1</a-select-option>
            <a-select-option key="1">2</a-select-option>
            <a-select-option key="2">3</a-select-option>
          </a-select>
          <template v-else="disabled">getProcessInfo</template>
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 2, 4].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="线径"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrLine']" placeholder="请输入线径"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="外径"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrOut']" placeholder="请输入外径"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 2, 3, 4].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="自由高度"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrHeight']" placeholder="请输入自由高度"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 4].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="总圈数"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrTurns']" placeholder="请输入总圈数"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="材质"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrMaterial']" placeholder="请输入材质"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="表面处理"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
           <a-select
            v-if="disabled"
            allowClear
            placeholder="请输入表面处理"
            v-decorator="['productAttrSurface']"
          >
            <a-select-option key="0">0</a-select-option>
            <a-select-option key="1">1</a-select-option>
          </a-select>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 4].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="压并高度"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrPressure']" placeholder="请输入压并高度"/>

          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 3, 4].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="工作高度"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrWork']" placeholder="请输入工作高度"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 2].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="有效圈数"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrEffective']" placeholder="请输入有效圈数"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 2, 4, 5].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="力值"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrStrength']" placeholder="请输入力值"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 2, 4].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="旋向"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-select
            v-if="disabled"
            allowClear
            placeholder="请输入旋向"
            v-decorator="['productAttrRotating']"
          >
            <a-select-option key="0">正旋</a-select-option>
            <a-select-option key="1">反旋</a-select-option>
          </a-select>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="螺旋角"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrSpiralAngle']" placeholder="请输入螺旋角"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 2, 4].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="展开长度"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrOnlength']" placeholder="请输入展开长度"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[3, 4, 5].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="内径"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrInner']" placeholder="请输入内径"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[3, 5].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="厚度"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrThickness']" placeholder="请输入厚度"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[4].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="波数"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrWave']" placeholder="请输入波数"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[4].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="层数"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrLayer']" placeholder="请输入层数"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 3, 4].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="应力"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrStress']" placeholder="请输入应力"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 3, 4, 5].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="刚度"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrStiffness']" placeholder="请输入刚度"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 3, 4].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="最大变形量"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrDeformation']" placeholder="请输入最大变形量"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
      <a-col :span="8" v-if="[0, 1, 2, 4].includes(springVal)">
        <a-form-item
          label="旋绕比"
          :class="{labelColor: isLabelColor}"
          :label-col="labelCol"
          :wrapper-col="wrapperCol"
        >
          <a-input v-if="disabled" v-decorator="['productAttrRotate']" placeholder="请输入旋绕比"/>
          <!-- <template v-else="disabled">{{getProcessInfo.code}}</template> -->
        </a-form-item>
      </a-col>
    </a-row>
  </a-form>
</template>
<script>
import { mixinBasic, mixinIsEdit } from '@/components/tools/mixin/mixin'

export default {
  name: 'ProcudtAttrForm',
  mixins: [mixinBasic, mixinIsEdit],
  data() {
    return {
      productAttrForm: this.$form.createForm(this),
      options: []
    }
  },
  props: {
    springVal: {
      type: Number,
      default: undefined
    }
  },
  created() {},
  methods: {}
}
</script>
<style lang="scss" scoped>
</style>
